value: Central America, South America: e Honduras to w, n Amazonia
Montane Evergreen Forest, Tropical Lowland Evergreen Forest, Secondary Forest (300-1400 m; upper Tropical and Subtropical zones, rarely lower Tropical Zone).

Canopy & edge of tall humid forest, tall second growth, tree plantations, shaded gardens, hedgerows;foothills & adjacent lowlands, mostly below 600m(Honduras);50-1200m (Costa Rica);400-1800m(Colombia);150-1900m(Venezuela)
